An artisan bakery that bakes fresh doughnuts, bread, muffins, tarts, and more in-store daily.
Health & Happiness – offers healthy nibbles for those wanting to snack responsibly.
The Streatery is a new all-day sit-down diner. It features a wide variety of delicious breakfasts, healthy quick lunches, Poké Bowls & salads, fresh sushi, wood-fired Neapolitan style pizzas, street foods, burgers and much more.
The in-store food offering includes Crispy Chicken, Pies, Pizzas, hot grab & go foods, and pre-packed sushi made fresh daily.
The Butchers Block and Braai Time offers an extensive range of the finest cuts of meat. Shoppers can expect 28-day aged Signature steak, a range of burger patties, sosaties, delicious roast meats, and premium pork. <img class="size-full wp-image-485409 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-6.jpg" alt="" width="1300" height="867" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-6.jpg 1300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-6-1200x800.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-485411 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-5.jpg" alt="" width="1300" height="867" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-5.jpg 1300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-5-1200x800.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px" /> <img class="size-full wp-image-485413 aligncenter" src="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-4.jpg" alt="" width="1300" height="867" srcset="https://businesstech.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Waterfall-Ridge-4.jpg 1300w, https://businesstech.co.za/new